a.n: Barbapapa - One Big Happy Family! I (12)

p.k:
The Cave Barbapapas / The Little Monsters The barbababies discover a strange cave. Barbalib tells the story of the caves Barbapapa and how they transformed.
The Barbababies have a sleepover in the living room. Fearing the monsters in the closet, they set up wacky traps to catch them (2020).
